er	jupati	jupaty	kaffir	kahikatea	kail	kaki	kalantas	kale	kali	kalmia	kalumpang	kanaf	kaoliang	kapok	kapuka	kauri	kaury	kawaka	kelpwort	kenaf	kentan	keteleeria	ketembilla	keurboom	khesari	kiaat	kingcup	kingwood	kino	kiss-me-over-the-garden-gate	kitambilla	kitembilla	kitten-tails	kittul	kitul	kiwi	knapweed	knawe	knawel	kniphofia	knotgrass	kohleria	kohlrabi	kok-saghyz	kok-sagyz	kola	konini	kowhai	krigia	krubi	ku-chiku	kudzu	kumquat	kurakkan	kurchee	kurchi	kuri-chiku	kurrajong	kurrat	kweek	kyo-chiku	lacebark	lacepod	lady-of-the-night	lady-slipper	laelia	lambkill	lancewood	langsat	langset	lantana	larch	larkspur	latanier	lauhala	laurel	laurel-tree	laurelwood	lavender	lawyerbush	leadplant	leadwort	leatherleaf	leatherwood	lecanopteris	leek	legume	lemanderin	lemon	lemon-wood	lemongrass	lemonwood	lentil	lentisk	leopardbane	lepidobotrys	lespedeza	lettuce	leucothoe	liana	lichee	licorice	life-of-man	lightwood	lignosae	lilac	liliopsid	lily	lilyturf	lime	linden	ling	lingberry	lingenberry	lingonberry	liparis	lipfern	liquidambar	liquorice	litchi	lithophyte	lithops	live-and-die	live-forever	livelong	liverleaf	loasa	lobelia	locoweed	locust	lodgepole	loganberry	logwood	lomatia	longan	longanberry	longroot	lontar	loofah	loosestrife	loquat	lords-and-ladies	lotus	lovage	love-in-a-mist	love-in-idleness	love-in-winter	love-lies-bleeding	lucerne	luffa	lumbermill	lungen	lupin	lupine	lychnis	lycopod	lyre-flower	lyreflower	macadamia	macamba	macrozamia	madake	madder	madderwort	madnep	madrona	madrono	madwort	magnolia	magnoliopsid	maguey	mahagua	mahoe	mahogany	mahuang	maidenhair	maikoa	maize	majagua	makomako	malanga	maleberry	mallee	mallow	malope	malvasia	mamey	mammee	mammillaria	mamoncillo	man-of-the-earth	mandarin	mandioc	mandioca	mandrake	mangel-wurzel	manglietia	mango	mangold	mangold-wurzel	mangosteen	mangrove	manioc	manroot	manufactory	manzanita	maple	maquiladora	marang	maranta	marasca	maravilla	marble-wood	marblewood	margosa	marguerite	marigold	marihuana	marijuana	mariposa	marjoram	markweed ie	softy	soja	sojourner	solan	solarium	solderer	soldier	soldier-fish	soldierfish	sole	solenogaster	solenoid	solicitor	solitaire	solitary	solitudinarian	solleret	soloist	solon	solver	soma	soman	sombrero	somebody	someone	sommelier	somnambulist	somniloquist	son	son-in-law	sonar	songbird	songbook	songster	songstress	songwriter	sonneteer	sonny	sonogram	sonograph	sonometer	soothsayer	soph	sophist	sophisticate	sophomore	soprano	sorb	sorcerer	sorceress	sordino	sorehead	sorgho	sorghum	sorgo	sorrel	sorrower	sort	sorter	sorus	sot	souari	soubrette	souk	soul	soundboard	soundbox	sounder	soundman	soundtrack	soup-fin	soup-strainer	soupfin	soupspoon	source	sourdine	sourdough	sourpuss	soursop	sourwood	sousaphone	souse	souslik	soutache	soutane	southernwood	southpaw	sovereign	sow	sowbane	sowbread	sower	soy	soya	soybean	spa	space	spacecraft	spaceman	spaceship	spacesuit	spacewalker	spackle	spade	spadefish	spadefoot	spadix	spammer	span	spandex	spandrel	spandril	spangle	spaniel	spanker	spanner	spar	spare	sparer	sparid	sparker	sparkleberry	sparkler	sparling	sparrow	spastic	spat	spathe	spathiphyllum	spatterdock	spatula	spawn	spawner	speakeasy	speaker	speakerphone	spear	spearfish	spearhead	spearmint	specialiser	specialist	specializer	specifier	specimen	speck	speckle	specs	spectacle	spectacles	spectator	spectrogram	spectrograph	spectrometer	spectrophotometer	spectroscope	speculator	speculum	speechifier	speechmaker	speechwriter	speedboat	speedometer	speedskater	speedway	speedwell	spelaeologist	speleologist	spell-checker	spellbinder	speller	spelt	spelunker	spend-all	spender	spendthrift	sperm	spermatid	spermatocide	spermatocyte	spermatophyte	spermatozoan	spermatozoid	spermatozoon	spermicide	spermophile	spewer	sphagnum	sphecoid	sphere	spherocyte	spherometer	sphingid	sphinx	sphygmomanometer	spic	spiceberry	spicebush	spicemill	spick	spider	spiderflower	spiderwort	spigot	spik	spike	spikemoss	spikenard	spile	spill	spiller	spillikin	spillway	spin-off	spinach	spindle	spindleberry	spindlelegs	spindleshan
